title: At Work, Dress Like Mark Zuckerberg or Steve Jobs?
text:
At Work, Dress Like Mark Zuckerberg or Steve Jobs? By Share Are the dress codes for job interviews changing? In a world where tech companies set standards, should you dress like Mark Zuckerberg or Steve Jobs? The Moneyologist weighs in on Lunch Break With Tanya Rivero.
